descriptionHtml:

• Get Detailed IFSC information

• IFSC Information just few clicks away

• Get instant alert within app when New App Update is available

• User Friendly Interface




What is IFS Code?

Indian Financial System Code is 11 digit alphanumeric unique code which is used to identify each branch of every bank in India. This code is given on the cheque book of a individuals, firms and corporates and is also required to transfer money through NEFT or RTGS
